!!What is _skopon_?

A simple, minimalistic Wiki written in 100% Dart.

!!Why on earth would I want to use such a thing?

Because (a) it helps you think better, (b) records thoughts and impressions, (c) it is the simplest form of database in today's advanced technological mire, (d) is a really cool programming exercise.

